<div class="card-project-list">

  <div class="card-part card-left flex-column" type="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#bloomModal">
    <div class="card-pic" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.01),rgba(0,0,0,0.01)), url('<%= image_path "bloom.jpg" %>')">
      <p class="card-title text-bfwp">Bloom</p>
      <%= link_to "https://bloom-rom1023.herokuapp.com/", target: "_blank", class: "card-icon i-link btml text-bfwp mr-1" do %>
        <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to "https://github.com/Rom1023/bloom", target: "_blank", class: "card-icon i-code btmr text-bfwp" do %>
        <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="card-desc">
      <p class="">A web application on which doctors can post rare patient cases and look for help. Other doctors, from different regions, can communicate and contribute to find the solution together.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="bloomModal" class="card-part card-right modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="bloomModalTitle" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered modal-lg" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 id="bloomModalTitle" class="modal-title">Bloom</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
          <div>
            <div class="card-s-title text-purple"><strong>Hightlighted Features</strong></div>
            <div>
              <%= link_to "https://bloom-rom1023.herokuapp.com/", target: "_blank", class: "card-icon i-link topl text-bfwp mr-1" do %>
                <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
              <% end %>
              <%= link_to "https://github.com/Rom1023/bloom", target: "_blank", class: "card-icon i-code topr text-bfwp" do %>
                <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-purple-d">Ruby | Ruby on Rails | Cloudinary | PG search | Action Cable | Redis</p>
          <p>With the app, doctors can create anonymous cases for patients to look for help, add case descriptions and attach medical reports as supporting documents, build projects with medical cases, search available cases/projects by keywords, comment on projects and link their own case to other doctorsâ€™ projects.</p>
          <ul>
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>Action Cable</strong> enables new messages be broadcasted to all subcribed users. The message will appear immedately on users' ends, without refreshing the page.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><strong>PG search</strong> provides search function based on PostgreSQL's full text search. It enables keywords search through customizable scopes.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

